Yanked

APRIL 17, 2015, 4:00pm EST

Welcome to Yanked! Pet Skills, the only live, interactive pet talent show on the internet!

Talented pets compete live from home or the dog park via webcams, iPhones and iPads. Viewers watch on their internet-connected devices and vote on the acts, narrowing down the performances until there’s a winner.

If you have a pet who can do fun tricks, or love supercute animals, this is the show for you!

Show auditions are MARCH 20, 2015
